data.description: Nestled amidst the tranquil beauty of nature, this 5-bedroom home is waiting to be discovered. Set on a sprawling 2.2-acre lot in a picturesque equestrian-friendly community, this property offers a unique blend of serenity and potential, making it the perfect canvas for your dream lifestyle. The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, offering ample counter space, and a convenient layout that makes meal preparation a breeze. The living room overlooks the backyard sanctuary, a perfect retreat for relaxation and entertainment. You'll be wowed by impressive 1500 sqft workshop situated in the backyard. This versatile space is perfect for hobbyists, DIY enthusiasts, or anyone in need of extra storage. With some TLC to reach its full potential, this home presents a remarkable opportunity that can be transformed into luxurious retreat that perfectly suits your lifestyle. Embrace the freedom of country living while enjoying the convenience of close shopping, dining, and entertainment.
